channel.description: Looking for an epic Minecraft experience? You were searching for a true anarchy survival server but couldn't find one? Maybe after many days you finally found one but it had 10 slots or it was extremely laggy? Look no further! If you want a real SMP experience, with lots of cool plugins and NO RULES, then this server is for you. Lead your faction to glory on www.verincraft.com
